# Proxy JNE candidate photos server-side (bypasses CORS)
# mpesije uses clean path-based URLs, less Imperva friction than votoinformado
# IMPORTANT: jpeg rule must come BEFORE the jpg catch-all
/foto-proxy-jpeg/*  https://mpesije.jne.gob.pe/apidocs/:splat.jpeg  200!
/foto-proxy/*       https://mpesije.jne.gob.pe/apidocs/:splat.jpg   200!
